This person first said that she heard no EVP from you and then said that the lower spirits were messing with you.  Contradiction, debunking or no. I don&#39;t pay attention to people who say they can read your vibes--ridiculous- -some of the vibes they&#39;ve &quot;read&quot; have been only to serve themselves, as we all know.  I also understand how you would want to continue the interaction- -I would, too, if I found myself in a similar predicament.  I try not to go there, although it has happened.  Keep us posted.  

